Sentencas: We describe the preparation, electrochemical and structural properties of the thin film Y-stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ), of interest for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) at an operating temperature of 800 degreesC. Thin films of YSZ were prepared by reactive sputtering deposition of Zr-Y targets in Ar-O-2 mixture atmospheres.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: The thickness of the YSZ film, deposited onto the porous NiO-YSZ substrates, is approximately 8 mum.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: The microstructure of the YSZ film was investigated using scanning electron microscope.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: The electrochemical properties of a thin film cell Ag/NiO-YSZ/YSZ/Ag were studied using impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: The electrolyte and electrode (substrate) resistances were measured under different atmospheres as a function of temperature.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: Above 600 degreesC the ohmic resistance of the cermet electrode (substrate) is comparable to the ionic resistance of the solid electrolyte.
Titulo: Electrical and microstructural investigations of cermet anode/YSZ thin film systems

Sentencas: This is probably influenced by the cermet electrode microstructure.
